{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 3}
The bells will all be ringing
And all the fires will be [G7]aglow
And our hearts will all be singing
As we go gliding through the [C]snow
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 4}
Yes we're going to build a snowman
